data.description: Welcome to the jewel of the real estate market: a spectacular townhouse that redefines elegance and comfort. This 4 bedroom, 3 full bathroom residence has been meticulously remodeled to offer a modern and sophisticated lifestyle. Enjoy the convenience of a private garage and be captivated by the charm of the covered patio, a contemporary oasis that includes a full kitchen to delight your guests. The outdoor space is simply spectacular, designed to spend unforgettable family afternoons. This property represents the perfect fusion between luxury and functionality, offering a home where every detail has been carefully considered to create an exceptional living experience. Discover elegance in every corner and make this townhouse your new home!
